  "title": "喜欢和渴望所涉及的神经回路",
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"VYUjuVVk\">刺激食物摄入的阿片类回路分布广泛，而享乐型「喜欢」回路则更为集中，主要分布在伏隔核的喙状壳中。</p><hr/><p data-pid=\"nizGAuU6\">引用的摘录来自以下<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/References\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">参考资料</a>：</p><p data-pid=\"jzRlucdB\">标题：外侧伏隔核中的愉悦热点：μ-阿片受体在何处增加甜味的愉悦影响？</p><p data-pid=\"_rQuCutG\">作者：Susana Peciña 和 Kent C. Berridge</p><p data-pid=\"S_9pqhO3\">日期：2005 年</p><p data-pid=\"DbkuSwr9\">反向链接：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Pleasure_of_learning\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">学习的乐趣</a><sup data-text=\"学习的乐趣\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/602150910\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup></p><p data-pid=\"ihoFyg2Z\">链接：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.jneurosci.org/content/25/50/11777.long\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">http://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">jneurosci.org/content/2</span><span class=\"invisible\">5/50/11777.long</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"qJdVDfe9\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 <span class=\"nolink\">Shom</span>，校对 Jarrett Ye<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Neural_circuits_involved_in_liking_and_wanting\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Neural circuits involved in liking and wanting - supermemo.guru</a><br/>本<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/References\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">参考资料</a>用于注释《<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=ht